{"tid":642991,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【長雄遭淋紅油】毛記保薦人長雄 上市後沽了99%持股","createTime":"2018-04-26T07:37:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-26T08:01:57.000Z","uid":84840,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8cf587f3ec5b6ae1b8d6fa31bde6eaf32b5be2d4","tid":642991,"uid":84840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:37:50.000Z","msg":"今早位於中區德輔道中的長雄證券，其招牌遭兩名男子淋潑紅油。長雄證券的「揸弗人」，是人稱「大凌張」的張志誠，最近得意之作是成為毛記葵涌的保薦人，該股以1.2元上市，掛牌當日一度升至11.76元，直至現在回落至3.47元，帶挈林日曦、阿Bu及陳強3位毛記創辦人晉身億萬富豪。<br />\n<br />\n毛記上市首日，長雄證券仍持有334萬股或1.23%毛記股權，但其後沽了99%持股，目前已沽剩3.2萬股。<br />\n<br />\n有冇高j傻散出黎認𣺉紅油<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88361cc9cc7fb6f67c977b73ba8a1614269c60db","tid":642991,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7243de8303761867333c27dc645757df1ca8c108","tid":642991,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食完人血饅頭<br />\n公司高層已經上哂車<br />\n真係多謝哂12$接貨果班"},{"pid":"99f041e7ced064c9d8c93d4e0278124b4a0ad30d","tid":642991,"uid":84840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7243de8303761867333c27dc645757df1ca8c108","tid":642991,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:38:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 食完人血饅頭<br />\n公司高層已經上哂車<br />\n真係多謝哂12$接貨果班"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-26T07:41:52.000Z","msg":"貪心的小狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n接人火棒條氣唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329bc4a6610cbed29b4ec301e8feaf3a37ce7cc2","tid":642991,"uid":97,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,